---
---
<section>
  <div class="inner">
    <img src="/images/nxsinformatics.png" alt="NXS Informatics" class="logo" />
    <h1>Benvenuto su NXSHUB</h1>
    <p class="sub">Risorse, strumenti e community per il tuo server Minecraft, tutto in un posto solo.</p>
    <div class="btns">
      <a href="#" class="primary"><i class="bx bx-store"></i> Shop</a>
      <a href="#" class="ghost"><i class="bx bx-grid-alt"></i> Risorse</a>
      <a href="#" class="ghost"><i class="bx bxl-discord-alt"></i> Discord</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    padding: 10rem 1.5rem 5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .inner {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .logo {
    height: 80px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }
  .sub {
    color: var(--text2);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .btns {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btns a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.65rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .primary {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
  }
  .ghost {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .ghost:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
</style>
